news_header: Kamala Harris congratulated Donald Trump on his election win.
news_text: Doic presidential candidate Kamala Harris has called Republican Donald Trump to congratulate him on winning the election, according to Reuters. Trump received 291 electoral votes, while Harris received 223. Harris' assistant stated that the call emphasized the importance of a peaceful transition and that the president serves all Americans. Harris is scheduled to speak at Howard University in Washington on Wednesday evening.
